<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>第二位男嘉宾陈晓阳今年</span>22 <span>岁，来自福州，现居上海。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>男嘉宾说，自己很少在朋友圈和社交软件发布内容，他</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>喜欢</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>听摇滚、收藏</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>黑胶唱片，旅行时</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不会花时间打卡网红景点，而是走街串巷地寻找</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>地道美食。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>女嘉宾彭小溪果断爆灯，她说，男嘉宾一出场就吸引住了她的目光，男嘉宾的外貌正是自己的理想型，安静随和的性格更让她心动。</span></span></p>
<p><iframe allowfullscreen="" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=q3161f2l56a"></iframe></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>男嘉宾和前任在朋友聚会上结识，彼此都是一眼心动，明知异国恋的未来还是勇敢走到了一起。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>但</span>15 <span>个小时的</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>时差</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>隔离了</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>两人</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>的情绪交流</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，长久以往，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>太疲惫</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>的两人最终无奈</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>分手。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>男嘉宾还需要完成一年的海外学业，女嘉宾汪晶提问，</span></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>男嘉宾上一段</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>恋爱</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>失败</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>就是因为异国，</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>现在</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>不怕重蹈覆辙吗？</span></span></strong></p>
