<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>男嘉宾会作何回答？他是否会和爆灯女生牵手离开？</span></span></p>
<p><strong>家务我来做！</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>第三位男嘉宾杨迪今年</span>27 <span>岁，来自广西，是一名小学教师。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>男嘉宾表示，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>家务做饭</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>自己</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>都</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>愿意</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>承包</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，自己有</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>一点强迫症和洁癖</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，对另一半的要求就是尽量不要弄乱自己的布置，享受回家时饭菜温热、一切井井有条的舒适就好。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>少年时父亲的离世让自己很早地承担了照顾家庭的责任，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>而母亲</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>对另一半的要求</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>也很简单</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>只要</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>孝顺</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>长辈就可以</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><iframe allowfullscreen="" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=z316111zeyc"></iframe></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>男嘉宾</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>在</span>VCR <span>里提到了</span><span>“</span><span>不走寻常路</span><span>”</span><span>的女嘉宾</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>樊蝶，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>他说，樊蝶直爽的</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>性格是自己的理想型，但</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>她的</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>长相</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>确实不是自己的菜。不过男嘉宾真诚表示，如果樊蝶你出道，我绝对当你的广西粉丝后援会副会长！</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201017/1c9e5a05bec544ae84b42832bc11ce9b.gif" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>女嘉宾张伊菲</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>说</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>自己</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>对性格好的男生</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>完全</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>没有抵抗力，喜欢做家务让她</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>对男嘉宾</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>的好感更上一层楼。但是自己生活在南京，</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>和男嘉宾离得很远怎么办</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>？男嘉宾</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>的回答非常直白果断，</span></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>自己去喜欢的人的城市生活，异地恋问题就迎刃而解了。</span></span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201017/7294557177d345eba71f05a6540cb195.gif" /></p>
